name: Custom Name
description:
These wooden wall letters are hand painted to compliment your child's space. Painted with care to add to your theme, or designed with love to build your theme around!

Painted just for your little one. They are one of a kind, shouldn't their room be too?

Available in 6", 8" or 10". 

Please contact seller before purchase to discuss font and size.

name: Growth Chart
description:
They grow so fast... a treasured memento to keep track of your little ones growth!

Our charts are hand painted and one of a kind. You chose your colors and/or theme. These canvas are attached together by matching ribbons, so they are easily folded together when needed to be stored.

Please contact seller before purchase to discuss design.

name: Storage Step Stool
description:
Little one's will be able to brush their teeth and wash their hands without assistance, they'll feel so big! 

Each stool is an original hand-painted design.

This sturdy step stool is perfect keepsake.

Please contact seller before purchase to discuss design.

name: Bow Holder
description:
Display your daughters hair bows in style with these hand painted bow holders. 

Choose from scalloped plaque or ballerina tutu design, with matching ribbons attached to store her hair accessories.

Please contact seller before purchase to discuss design.

name: Accessories
description:
Knobs and Switch plates... Accessories, Accessories, Accessories!

Everyone knows it's important to accessorize! 

Our wooden dresser knobs  and switch plates are hand painted to compliment any space. Just a small touch that will completely change the feel of your child's room. They are sure to add a sassy touch to any room!

Knobs - $3.00ea
Switch plates - $12.00ea

Please contact seller before purchase to discuss design.
